Evolution
Pokedex

Egg group - DRAGON

Its shell is terrifically heavy and hard. Few Ovarapt attain the strength to break out of it. It hunts in tandem with other Ovarapt, using cunning and traps.
Its small stature frequently causes prey to underestimate it. Velokota is quite smart. Packs of them are terrifically dangerous due to their advanced tactics.
Its significant bulk slows it down, but allows it to predate upon {POKEMON} several times its size. A thin layer of corundrum makes its hide extra durable.
